        "title": "fix(ci): repair current main checks",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- tolerates missing session-store maps while building single-row child-session candidate indexes\n- prevents `chat.history` / session-info paths from throwing when a caller has no loaded store but still asks for child-session metadata\n- updates the stale Talk launch-options UI test to exercise the current custom Talk select controls instead of removed native `<select>` controls\n- tightens the compaction-rotation attempt mock/result fixture types so the current core test typecheck passes\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/agent-command.compaction-rotation.test.ts src/gateway/session-utils.test.ts ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts --reporter=dot`: passed 3 shards / 178 tests on current branch after rebasing onto `origin/main` `015c6b40aea`\n- `node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check --threads=1 src/agents/agent-command.compaction-rotation.test.ts src/gateway/session-utils.ts ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts`: passed\n- `node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs src/agents/agent-command.compaction-rotation.test.ts src/gateway/session-utils.ts ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts`: passed\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`: passed\n- AWS Crabbox: `node scripts/crabbox-wrapper.mjs run --provider aws --label main-ci-repair-rebased-check-changed --shell -- \"pnpm check:changed\"` (`provider=aws`, `lease=cbx_a6fbd8a6a9db`, `slug=blue-barnacle-a87c`, `run=run_4c637cf49fd6`, exit 0)\n- GitHub PR checks on head `8d5ea60e441bf96be557200682d7f9d76098b49b`: passed; latest poll reported no failed or running checks\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: the gateway no longer throws `Cannot convert undefined or null to object` while building single-row child-session candidates for session-info paths that do not have a loaded store, and the current Talk launch-options plus compaction-rotation test drift no longer block CI.\n\nReal environment tested: linked OpenClaw gwt worktree `fix-main-ci-blockers-20260601` rebased onto current `origin/main`, AWS Crabbox Linux changed-gate proof, and GitHub PR CI on the pushed head.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: reran the focused session-utils regression file, compaction-rotation test, full chat view test file, formatter, lint, diff check, remote `pnpm check:changed`, and GitHub PR checks.\n\nEvidence after fix: the focused gateway shard passed 104 tests; the compaction-rotation shard passed 3 tests; the chat view shard passed 71 tests including the previously failing Talk launch-options test; AWS Crabbox changed gate selected `core` and `coreTests` and exited 0; GitHub PR checks are green.\n\nObserved result after fix: missing stores produce an empty child-session candidate map instead of throwing, valid store callers keep the same candidate and context-token behavior, the Talk launch-options test now exercises the shipped custom select controls, and the compaction-rotation fixture now matches the runtime attempt/result types.\n\nWhat was not tested: full repository suite locally.\n",
